<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="board-v">board <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɔːd/    美 /bɔːrd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>登上 (船 / 车 / 飞机)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a boarding card / pass
登机牌</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Your plane <strong>is</strong> now <strong>boarding</strong> at Gate 7. 
您乘坐的航班正在7号登机口登机。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Six months ago Xie Lei said goodbye to her family and friends in China and boarded a plane for London. 
6个月前，谢蕾告别了中国的家人和朋友，登上了前往伦敦的飞机。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 5</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>寄宿：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>boarding school</strong> 
寄宿学校</p></div></div>